    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地狱是满员的，冥务是永恒的，而你就是掌控一切的主管！走进充满黑色幽默的策略和管理模拟游戏《罪托邦》，打理冥界功能最失调的惩戒教育所。你刚刚获得晋升，成为了地狱股份有限公司中级管理层的一员。你的职责很简单：让灵魂接受“再教育”，复活符合条件的灵魂。谁说被打进永恒地狱就不能优化流程赚大钱了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造处理罪孽的设施和建筑，完善自动化流程，管理手下的“冥务员”，同时帮助凡界持续繁荣发展……或者发动神力，让凡界的小人“豆仁”看看谁才是老大！掌控地狱各层，塑造冥界帝国。你想成为怎样的神？慈悲、高效还是小肚鸡肠……怎么选都看你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏关键特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>打造你的个性地狱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地狱的山峰幽穴、冰河火湖，都可以按照你最深、最黑暗的愿望定制！坠入地狱的灵魂源源不断，你需要打造运转流畅的冥界，才能高效处理！惩罚灵魂，赚取盈利，获得更强的能力或影响力。雇佣奇形怪状的冥务员，帮你处理海量的手续和文件……只要别拖欠他们的工资就行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/7b0e520d1dc58b5265d3d1f15db626ed.poster.avif?t=1772205511\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/7b0e520d1dc58b5265d3d1f15db626ed.webm?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/7b0e520d1dc58b5265d3d1f15db626ed.mp4?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>如其在上，如其在下</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凡界是冥界的基础，推动“在上”的繁荣发展，才能维持“在下”的复生循环。作为地狱大总管，你可以发动神力，“鼓励”豆仁更听话。小人懒懒散散？那怎么行——闪电和烈火伺候！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/20657f8d6b4c009cdf30324d72e463f1.poster.avif?t=1772205511\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/20657f8d6b4c009cdf30324d72e463f1.webm?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/20657f8d6b4c009cdf30324d72e463f1.mp4?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>七宗大罪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几番投胎下来，灵魂会积攒太多的罪孽。请密切关注罪孽的水平，打造专门的建筑加以净化，否则等到腐化爆发，恶煞肆虐，不仅效率会受打击，盈利也会受到负面影响……这可是比什么都可怕啊！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/317394b531e01b5f6ccc925b98e56070.poster.avif?t=1772205511\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/317394b531e01b5f6ccc925b98e56070.webm?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/317394b531e01b5f6ccc925b98e56070.mp4?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>魔鬼职场</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这才叫地狱难度的办公室政治！来剧情战役模式，见识一下圣经级别的公司权斗；来挑战模式，磨砺自己的管理上限；来沙盒模式，潜心钻研地狱建造美学，或心安理得地摆烂一整天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/e74ff2330616761c53fe0cd95e7b9999.poster.avif?t=1772205511\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/e74ff2330616761c53fe0cd95e7b9999.webm?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213700/extras/e74ff2330616761c53fe0cd95e7b9999.mp4?t=1772205511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
